{"tid":825773,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"上到大學 開始愈泥愈驚","createTime":"2018-09-17T19:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T19:48:41.000Z","uid":199869,"like":10,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f0deb48041827f52a5b625cedd466350488874e0","tid":825773,"uid":199869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T19:07:02.000Z","msg":"開學半個月 玩左幾個ocamp 平時又唔可以話摺到一個人坐 一個人食飯 一個人摺圖書館咁嘅 但係一有啲re-u 覺得自己總係格格不入咁 人地有講有笑 我就只可以一路聽一路傻笑 根本唔知比咩反應好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我都好想好似其他人咁多啲野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係佢地講嘅野好似同我唔啱channel咁 可能我真係中學太小圈子 玩泥玩去都係嗰堆 唔識同人相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能好多人話 開學幾個禮拜啫 遲下就會識到啱傾嘅人架啦 但萬一識唔到呢？咁咪一世就系度摺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n心底裏我係想active啲嘅 但我費事咁勉強啦 本身唔係咁多野講 格硬做出泥應該幾奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前ocamp都試過玩得放啲咁嘅 但係最後龜背啲人都係話我好靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  既然自己講咁多又攰 人地又話我係靜嘅咁就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人同我差唔多情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全能嘅連登仔可唔可以教下我點做 點先可以active啲 定keep住摺？做番自己嘅話我真係一句聲都唔出就算 但我討厭咁頹嘅自己<br />\n<br />\n利申真係正常樣 唔係油頭毒L 有玩樂器 遲啲pick up番運動"},{"pid":"d778e88210ff85e127367b6cfe83fc309445ec19","tid":825773,"uid":42374,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T19:09:05.000Z","msg":"泥你老母咩"},{"pid":"a823a3bdc7900a712854060dcc094a47bacccbea","tid":825773,"uid":199869,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"d778e88210ff85e127367b6cfe83fc309445ec19","tid":825773,"uid":42374,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T19:09:05.000Z","msg":"泥你老母咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T19:09:44.000Z","msg":"sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個正字係點？"},{"pid":"8eb939a1cde27949a4c249debbe3aeaca16bc34a","tid":825773,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T19:10:27.000Z","msg":"比我都驚啦 中文差成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea0abb441d493d6872f7fed72a8c2ef9c38b8968","tid":825773,"uid":200718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T19:11:30.000Z","msg":"Ching咩u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a931bcfbdc058ba9bc5835ae9a85d8b730791595","tid":825773,"uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T19:12:03.000Z","msg":"做女人囉"},{"pid":"e28007f600ccb2f9699f758ec6fad35879f6738e","tid":825773,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T19:12:31.000Z","msg":"講句嘢都驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0604ee1ab4c53b5d9291acbb6f49706e033ee223","tid":825773,"uid":129340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T19:12:50.000Z","msg":"搵返自己岩傾<br />\n組爸上莊都鳩鳩地 未必岩傾"},{"pid":"230def75cc5e4d73f340cb285a0ba4593fcc671b","tid":825773,"uid":134111,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T19:13:15.000Z","msg":"入到大學講野行為正正常常都會識到新朋友仔既 btw巴打讀咩科"},{"pid":"3e4f603a202956bde21547ea338aeb63a9d989e1","tid":825773,"uid":138102,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T19:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7fb84d4dae8e9ae71b16f46a4941fe321a687a7","tid":825773,"uid":4876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T19:14:25.000Z","msg":"泥你老母"},{"pid":"a1cdb33ccc889bc6d76adf0372447588be0db85b","tid":825773,"uid":199869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"230def75cc5e4d73f340cb285a0ba4593fcc671b","tid":825773,"uid":134111,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1